if it complains about fsgame.ltx missing, here's a way to fix it (works for me, and I think it should work for others aswell):

open up your notepad > type the following in there: start bin\xrengine > save this file as .bin file in your Game Directory (the name of it can be anything you wish, I named it start.bin)

then just run it, and it should be ok

